### 测试后端 API 接口

### 1. 创建订单
POST http://localhost:3000/api/order/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "Book001",
  "deviceId": "test_device_001",
  "imageUrl": null
}

### 2. 查询订单详情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/order/{{orderId}}

### 3. 查询订单列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/order?deviceId=test_device_001&page=1&limit=10

### 4. 更新订单图片
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/order/{{orderId}}/image
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/baby-photo.jpg"
}

### 5. 验证支付（Mock 收据）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/payment/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "receiptData": "mock-receipt-data-base64",
  "transactionId": "1000000123456789",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/baby-photo.jpg"
}

### 6. 查询任务状态
GET http://localhost:3000/api/task/{{taskId}}

### 7. 根据订单查询任务
GET http://localhost:3000/api/task/order/{{orderId}}

### 8. 取消任务
POST http://localhost:3000/api/task/{{taskId}}/cancel

### 9. 获取绘本下载信息
GET http://localhost:3000/api/book/{{orderId}}/download

### 10. 上传图片（multipart）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/upload/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="baby.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-baby.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 11. 删除临时图片
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/upload/image/baby-1234567890.jpg

### 12. Swagger 文档
GET http://localhost:3000/api/docs
